sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant UI as React Frontend<br/>(xterm.js)
    participant IPC as Tauri IPC
    participant PTY as PTY Manager<br/>(portable-pty)
    participant Shell as Shell Process<br/>(bash/zsh/fish)
    participant OSC as OSC 133 Parser
    participant Store as Block Store<br/>(Zustand)

    User->>UI: Keystroke
    UI->>IPC: invoke write_to_pty(session_id, bytes)
    IPC->>PTY: PtyPort.write_input(bytes)
    PTY->>Shell: Write to PTY master fd

    Note over Shell: Shell processes input,<br/>executes command

    Shell->>PTY: Write output to PTY slave
    PTY->>IPC: Read from PTY master fd
    IPC->>UI: emit pty_data(session_id, bytes)
    UI->>UI: xterm.js.write(bytes)
    UI->>OSC: Scan bytes for OSC 133

    alt Prompt Start (OSC 133 A)
        OSC->>Store: New block - state=prompting
    else Command Executed (OSC 133 C)
        OSC->>Store: Update block - state=running
    else Command Finished (OSC 133 D)
        OSC->>Store: Update block - state=completed, exit_code=N
    end

    Store->>UI: Re-render with block boundaries
